# About CodeIntegrity

CodeIntegrity is a technology company founded on January 1, 2024, with a focus on enhancing software security and integrity through innovative solutions. The company provides tools and services aimed at ensuring the reliability and safety of code, which is crucial for organizations that prioritize software security.

The company offers a range of services, including:

- Code analysis and review
- Security assessments
- Continuous integration and deployment support
- Custom software solutions

These services are designed to improve code quality and security, although specific product details were not provided in the available content.

CodeIntegrity serves a diverse clientele, including businesses from various sectors that prioritize software security and integrity in their operations. The company operates in a B2B model, providing its services to other businesses.

As of the latest available information, CodeIntegrity has not raised any funding, with a total of 0M USD reported as of December 6, 2024 [(Crunchbase, 2025)](https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/codeintegrity).

The company distributes its products and services through direct engagement with potential customers, who can book a time slot to discuss their needs directly with the team through their booking page [(Bookings)](https://outlook.office365.com/book/CodeIntegrity1@codeintegrity.ai).
